Initiate package json on this project: > npm init -y

create entry js file for this project: app.js

install express on this project : > npm install express --save

to spotreload and refresh the save code: > npm install nodemon --save-dev
after that add start in package.jon file the line is : in side the scripts -> "start":"nodemon app.js" .(her app.js is entry file name)

after that run > npm start

install body parser - npm install body-parser --save

npm install mongoose
